description:
A study of British women writers, often focusing on the women authors who came into prominence between 1775 and 1825. 

See the English Department's website at www.english.upenn.edu for a complete description of the current offerings.
name: BRITISH WOMEN WRITERS: 18TH CENT. WOMEN WRITERS
